{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2132, "height": 2893, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "四、家训格言", "block_bbox": [872, 263, 1183, 314], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "家训格言，是一个姓氏和家族文化传统的表现，杜姓的家训主要有二，一是杜甫示儿家训，二是山东滨州杜氏家族家训。其他杜姓家训散见于各地杜姓家谱之中。摘主要者录如下文，以为杜姓后裔所当牢记：", "block_bbox": [198, 408, 1759, 602], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "1.杜甫家训", "block_bbox": [295, 628, 518, 672], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜甫是唐朝大诗人，一生坎坷，诸子皆随他历尽艰辛，身逢乱世，不忘教子。这在他诸多示儿诗中随处可见。\n", "block_bbox": [201, 700, 1760, 822], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《宗武生日》诗：“小子何时见？高秋此日生。自从都邑语，已伴老夫名。诗是吾家事，人传世上情。熟精文选理，休觅彩衣轻。凋瘵筵初秩，欹斜坐不成。流霞分片片，涓滴就徐倾。”诗中，殷切希望儿子宗武要把世代读书做诗的家风传之久远，告诫其子要趁青春少年及早努力，这才是孝。", "block_bbox": [199, 849, 1763, 1115], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《又示宗武》诗：“觅句新知律，摊书解满床。试吟青玉案，莫羡紫罗囊。假日从时饮，明年共我长。应须饱经术，已似爱文章。十五男儿志，三千弟子行。曾参与游夏，达者得升堂。”诗中，告诫其子不要羡慕那些贵族子弟吃喝玩乐，悠闲度日，要有像孔子那样求学问道的精神，成为一个有精深造诣的人。杜甫训子不是简单说教，而据事明理，深入浅出地言传身教。这首诗满怀喜悦地称赞儿子已能写诗、写文章，并引用晋朝谢安善于用婉转的方法教育侄儿谢安的故事，勉励儿子敦品励行。\n", "block_bbox": [200, 1139, 1765, 1616], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《元日示宗武》诗“汝啼吾手战，吾笑汝身长。处处逢正月，迢迢滞远方。飘零还柏酒，衰病只藜床。训谕青衿子，名惭白首郎。赋诗犹落笔，献寿更称觞。不见江东弟，高歌泪数行。”\n", "block_bbox": [199, 1641, 1765, 1831], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《熟食日示宗文、宗武》：“消渴游江汉，羁栖尚甲兵。几年逢熟食，万里逼清明。松柏邛山路，风花白帝城。汝曹催我老，回首泪纵横。", "block_bbox": [202, 1858, 1765, 1978], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《又示两儿》：“令节成吾老，他时见汝心。浮生看物变，为恨与年深。长葛书难得，江州涕不禁。团圆思弟妹，行坐白头吟。\n", "block_bbox": [202, 2005, 1765, 2124], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "2.滨州杜氏述训", "block_bbox": [294, 2152, 619, 2196], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "山东滨州（今滨州市）杜氏家族有《石画龛论述》，杜愕等著，其中有《杜氏述训》48条。\n", "block_bbox": [203, 2223, 1767, 2343], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "第1则：自见之谓明，自听之谓聪，自胜之谓强。人惟不自见、自闻而后自是。既自是矣，长傲益怠，何有于强？乃所谓大愚也。子弟至是，父兄不以为忧而反为喜，其父兄亦大愚也。\n", "block_bbox": [200, 2368, 1767, 2563], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "第2则。先大夫每引《颜氏家训》教余兄弟，曰：“少成若天性，习惯如自", "block_bbox": [292, 2587, 1764, 2636], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1884, 768, 1964, 1506], "block_id": 13, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "三四四", "block_bbox": [1900, 2183, 1951, 2305], "block_id": 14, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.966948390007019, "coordinate": [200.87969970703125, 1139.572998046875, 1765.724365234375, 1616.201904296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9565364122390747, "coordinate": [199.48492431640625, 849.009033203125, 1763.9208984375, 1115.4366455078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9562320709228516, "coordinate": [200.66265869140625, 2368.994140625, 1767.73876953125, 2563.61767578125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9556797742843628, "coordinate": [198.5101318359375, 408.35565185546875, 1759.2205810546875, 602.2683715820312]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9524160027503967, "coordinate": [199.9442138671875, 1641.675537109375, 1765.554931640625, 1831.956298828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9397550821304321, "coordinate": [203.03094482421875, 2223.24609375, 1767.30615234375, 2343.697265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9336761832237244, "coordinate": [202.03448486328125, 1858.3740234375, 1765.42138671875, 1978.7626953125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9264206886291504, "coordinate": [201.7659912109375, 700.4100952148438, 1760.5582275390625, 822.9152221679688]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9260724782943726, "coordinate": [202.11126708984375, 2005.197998046875, 1765.813720703125, 2124.861083984375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8849743604660034, "coordinate": [295.792236328125, 628.0718994140625, 518.4588623046875, 672.7191162109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8721448183059692, "coordinate": [292.7313232421875, 2587.229248046875, 1764.0606689453125, 2636.271240234375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8297440409660339, "coordinate": [294.434326171875, 2152.31103515625, 619.1604614257812, 2196.65869140625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7790884375572205, "coordinate": [872.0169067382812, 263.42437744140625, 1183.779541015625, 314.10748291015625]}, {"cls_id": 18, "label": "aside_text", "score": 0.5908787250518799, "coordinate": [1900.99658203125, 2183.24267578125, 1951.592529296875, 2305.990234375]}, {"cls_id": 18, "label": "aside_text", "score": 0.5348408818244934, "coordinate": [1884.05517578125, 768.9769287109375, 1964.950927734375, 1506.2098388671875]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[875, 259], [1188, 262], [1187, 322], [874, 318]], [[299, 409], [1758, 409], [1758, 459], [299, 459]], [[209, 481], [1757, 480], [1757, 530], [209, 531]], [[210, 555], [1205, 555], [1205, 603], [210, 603]], [[298, 626], [516, 626], [516, 678], [298, 678]], [[298, 700], [1759, 700], [1759, 753], [298, 753]], [[1867, 751], [1980, 751], [1980, 1029], [186